name: a.lone X, 2021
description: "a.lone X, 2021" is the digital redux of an analog work, "a.lone, 2018". It is from a series of artworks entitled 'Heart Blob'. The source work is made with materials collected from walls in Los Angeles, Brooklyn & Madrid. 'a.lone,2018' was exhibited in 2019 as part of an installation commissioned by the the I.C.M.A. and E.P.A (Environmental Protection Agency). All artwork, digital manipulation and soundscape by codyfied.
